      <title>德国极右翼支持在欧洲大选前减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/german-far-right-support-dwindles-ahead-of-european-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在六月的欧洲议会选举之前，德国选择党的支持率进一步下降，但总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨的三路执政联盟仍在努力从极右翼政党的困境中获得任何优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/german-far-right-support-dwindles-ahead-of-european-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
